::KitKat::

She ran through the forest.  She saw the trees go by in a blurr as 
she ran past.  She had tears running down her cheeks as she ran.  She 
had pain in her chest,  it ws from the hurt she had for Land Mine.
She tried to out run the pain.  She dodged trees and fallen logs.  
She really didn't know where she was going or even cared.  Her hurt 
and pain was driving her. Everywhere she looked, she saw Land Mine.  
She felt her face feel cold as the wind touched her tears as they ran 
down her face.  

She kept running.  She had no idea where she was going, she just kept 
running.
